        "message": "=<p>I look forward to seeing you all for our check-in on {{ $json.meetingDate }} at {{ $json.meetingTime }}.</p>\n\n<p>To ensure we make the most of our time, please take a moment to review and update your <a href=\"https://www.notion.so/edscale/Individual-Task-Views-271d71fc6bb380c09425d89fade04621?source=copy_link\">Individual Task View</a>. Marking items as complete allows us to celebrate our wins and shifts our focus toward strategic next steps and how EdScale can best support you.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Pro-tip:</strong> Click the star icon in the top right corner to favorite your view for easy access!</p>\n\n<p>Kind regards,</p>\n\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color:rgb(136,136,136);font-size:12.8px\"><div style=\"font-family:tahoma,sans-serif;font-size:small;display:inline\">Sarah Sanchez-Leal, Education Analyst</div></div><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color:rgb(136,136,136);font-size:12.8px\"><div style=\"font-family:tahoma,sans-serif;font-size:small;display:inline\"><img data-aii=\"CiExYUwzRXNNWFR3QXlWNVFEekRiem9abVR3c0JHdmZaWDg\" src=\"https://ci3.googleusercontent.com/mail-sig/AIorK4x6l3WBSoTJmo9aSlhwhuSAoMTnt0EBQVrCp_lvf6m6o6El3nvnuSe47cBrQY69rFufi3v8pjFccGac\" data-os=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1aL3EsMXTwAyV5QDzDbzoZmTwsBGvfZX8\"></div></div><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color:rgb(136,136,136);font-size:12.8px\"><div style=\"font-family:tahoma,sans-serif;font-size:small;display:inline\"><div><span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://www.edscalellc.com/\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204)\" target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#351c75\">www.edscalellc.com</font></a><font color=\"#888888\"> | (512) 640-9657</font></span><font color=\"#888888\"></font></div><div><a href=\"https://tidycal.com/mp4podm\" target=\"_blank\">Book a Meeting with me! </a></div></div></div></div>",
