    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Zap #25+27: Sarah Prep Email Reminders\n**Consolidation of Zap #25 (Implementation Session) + Zap #27 (CTE Monthly)**\nMirrors Zap #8 Coaching Prep Reminder pattern.\n\n### Flow:\n1. Schedule Every Minute\n2. Notion getAll — MAIN Tasks filtered by Prep Status = 'SEND Email', Status != Done, Lead contains Sarah\n3. Code — extract recipients (filter edscalellc), format date/time, determine path by title prefix\n4. Switch — route by title prefix:\n   - starts with 'Implementation Session' → Implementation email\n   - starts with 'CTE Monthly' → Monthly Check-in email\n5. Gmail — send the matching email (from Sarah)\n6. Notion — update Prep Status → 'Email sent'\n\n### SETUP NEEDED:\n- Connect Sarah's Gmail OAuth2 credential on both Gmail nodes",
        "height": 420,
        "width": 540
      },
